data.description: Move in ready! Turn key, this house is built solid! Beautifully updated three bedroom house is immaculate with upstairs loft, basement, extra large garage, fully fenced in yard with built in fire pit and large deck with covered porch. Fresh paint through entire house, new carpet in main floor bedrooms, newer floors, and all new door knobs and locks, kitchen includes Samsung 5 burner stove with griddle and air fryer oven is a chefs dream! Easy access to Hwy 6 and I65 makes conveniant to get anywhere.This charming house will not last long. It is a must see!
